reviews.text: I always enjoy my trips to Rye River Social! This was my first time checking out the brunch menu. It was so hard to choose my entree because everything...

A delicious and quick brunch!

The Breakfast Burrito was delicious, but what was really great was the side of smashed crispy potatoes that come with it....

Originally came in as an accident, our original destination was closed, and this was open and down the street.

The host greeted us, and sat us...
